<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us - Knowledge Hub</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-purple-50 min-h-screen px-6 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-blue-700 mb-6">About Knowledge Hub</h1>
    
    <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6 text-center">
      Empowering developers through a collaborative platform to learn, share, and grow together.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-10">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-4">What is Knowledge Hub?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Knowledge Hub is an open community where developers of all levels can ask questions, share answers,
          and build their skills. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned coder, this platform is built to
          help you grow.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We believe in the power of community-driven learning. With features like leaderboards, badges, and
          personalized profiles, contributing becomes rewarding and fun!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide a friendly space to ask programming questions</li>
          <li>Encourage collaborative learning and mutual growth</li>
          <li>Highlight expert contributors with recognition and badges</li>
          <li>Keep improving through community feedback</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-3">Meet the Team</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Built by passionate students and developers who love sharing knowledge.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Sakshi Singh" class="rounded-full mx-auto mb-2">
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Sakshi Singh</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Developer & Designer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Team Member" class="rounded-full mx-auto mb-2">
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Ankit Mehra</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Frontend Specialist</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
